A state of connector wave
==========================
All most all human get experienced about connector of wave in their life. It is just like by connecting two (-ve and +ve charge) wires of electric through bulb/fan/electronic device.
When you connect simply two wired through bulb you never get light in bulb since it is not the wire but the energy flow in wire make the bulb light.

When one bulb have current and another bulb have earthing and if these two get connected through bulb, you get light in bulb. It is the current/energy flow in wire get transformed
into light. If you connect two wire having one electric current(stream of electron) and one earthing wire simply you get short. Ie the bulb/electric device also play some important
role for transformation of electric energy in to light/mechanical movement.

Similar ways when you keep some charge(incomplete knowledge) in your mind/observation the same charge try to flow for its stability and when it get some flexible energy that can make it stable, 
it get connected with them and complete its incomplete circle.
How the charge in mind/observation look the flexible waves the base of looking of flexible wave is nothing but the connector waves.

How connector waves works?
--------------------------------------
The connector waves is taking important role for connecting the tow incomplete cycle of waves, it makes transformation of two incomplete waves into another complete waves.
Here our mind makes the incomplete waves due to poor understanding and the same state of mind searching the another waves of its completion.

Ex-
When you have knowledge about some realization/ state/ country/human/object/energy..so on and you have some confident(light confidence ie natural) about this then your state of mind is in search of confident of the same knowledge, when you read some book/listen some audio/video..so on that makes you stable.
Here your mind/observation have some incomplete state of energy/waves and similar types of waves hidden in emotion of the latter of books/audio/video and when you gone through of 
the same you get confidence that is completion of waves.

Here the video/books/audio play the role of connector of waves.

Ex-
When you get knowledge about spiritual life, you realize it is fantastic, this you incomplete waves in you state of mind about spiritual life but when you stat practicing meditation
/breathing yoga/silence your half waves get completed with your within energy transformation.

Here when you get the knowledge about spiritual life that is incomplete state of waves, the prating meditation/yoga/silence is the connector waves and energy/waves/feeling/realization get created is another half cycle of waves who makes your previous understanding(incomplete of waves) get completed.

***Every incomplete cycle of waves are in search of another similar/flexible half cycle of waves through connector waves***  
